### ────────────────────────────────────────────
### pigeonMQ REST API — IntelliJ HTTP Client
### Swagger UI: http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui
### OpenAPI:    http://localhost:8080/api-docs
### ────────────────────────────────────────────


### ═══════════════ HEALTH ═══════════════

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: application/json


### ═══════════════ TOPICS ═══════════════

### Create topic "orders"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name": "orders"}

### Create topic "notifications"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name": "notifications"}

### List all topics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/topics
Accept: application/json

### Get topic details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/topics/orders
Accept: application/json

### Delete topic
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/topics/notifications
Accept: application/json


### ═══════════════ QUEUES ═══════════════

### Create FIFO queue "emails"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/queues
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name": "emails", "mode": "FIFO"}

### Create PRIORITY queue "tasks"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/queues
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name": "tasks", "mode": "PRIORITY"}

### List all queues
GET http://localhost:8080/api/queues
Accept: application/json

### Get queue details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/queues/emails
Accept: application/json

### Delete queue
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/queues/tasks
Accept: application/json


### ═══════════════ VALIDATION / ERRORS ═══════════════

### 404: Get non-existent topic
GET http://localhost:8080/api/topics/nonexistent
Accept: application/json

### 400: Create topic with blank name
POST http://localhost:8080/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name": ""}

### 400: Create queue with invalid mode
POST http://localhost:8080/api/queues
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"name": "test", "mode": "LIFO"}

### 404: Delete non-existent queue
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/queues/nonexistent
Accept: application/json
